      "message": "This seems more like an implementation specific detail so I moved it (linux implementation doesn\u0027t use it)\n\nThe problem with 2ms was that this was causing the timeout of 500ms to take something like 4 seconds.  In the worst case where a users system could not start the crash service, the emulator boot time would always be delayed for that extra time.",
